questionnaireData.siteVision: To provide a tranquil and enjoyable experience for visitors in Pismo Beach, showcasing the beauty and attractions of the area while ensuring excellent customer care.
questionnaireData.uniqueQualities: A focus on relaxation and enjoyment with a beachside atmosphere, offering personalized experiences and services.
questionnaireData.primaryAudience: Families and individuals looking for a vacation or getaway in Pismo Beach.
questionnaireData.secondaryAudience: Tourists, adventure seekers, and local residents seeking leisure activities and accommodations.
questionnaireData.demographics: All ages, primarily families, couples, and individuals seeking relaxation and exploration.
questionnaireData.writingStyle: Engaging, friendly, and inviting, with a focus on creating a welcoming atmosphere.
questionnaireData.preferredPhotographyStyle: Bright, vibrant images showcasing the beauty of Pismo Beach and its attractions.
